data.inputSetTemplateYaml:
pipeline:
  identifier: "testPipeline_Cypress"
  stages:
  - stage:
      identifier: "CI_Stage1"
      type: "CI"
      spec:
        execution:
          steps:
          - step:
              identifier: "RunStep"
              type: "Run"
              spec:
                connectorRef: "<+input>"
                image: "<+input>"
                command: "<+input>"
                privileged: "<+input>"
                reports:
                  type: "JUnit"
                  spec:
                    paths: "<+input>"
                envVariables: "<+input>"
                outputVariables: "<+input>"
                runAsUser: "<+input>"
                resources:
                  limits:
                    memory: "<+input>"
                    cpu: "<+input>"
              description: "<+input>"
              timeout: "<+input>"
